  "sn56.13:1.1": "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56",
  "sn56.13:2.1": "2. Dhammacakkappavattanavagga",
  "sn56.13:3.1": "13. Khandhasutta",
  "sn56.13:4.1": "“Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, ariyasaccāni.",
  "sn56.13:4.2": "Katamāni cattāri?",
  "sn56.13:4.3": "Dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, <span class=\\\"var\\\" title=\\\"dukkhasamudayo ariyasaccaṃ dukkhanirodho ariyasaccaṃ (bj, s1-3)\\\" id=\\\"note526\\\">dukkhasamudayaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhanirodhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ</span> dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ.",
  "sn56.13:5.1": "Katamañca, bhikkhave, dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ?",
  "sn56.13:5.2": "‘Pañcupādānakkhandhā’ tissa vacanīyaṃ, <span class=\\\"var\\\" title=\\\"katame pañca? seyyathīdaṃ (bj) | katame pañca (s1-3, km) | seyyathīdaṃ (pts1)\\\" id=\\\"note527\\\">seyyathidaṃ</span>—",
  "sn56.13:5.3": "rūpupādānakkhandho … pe …",
  "sn56.13:5.4": "viññāṇupādānakkhandho.",
  "sn56.13:5.5": "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ.",
  "sn56.13:6.1": "Katamañca, bhikkhave, dukkhasamudayaṃ ariyasaccaṃ?",
  "sn56.13:6.2": "Yāyaṃ taṇhā ponobbhavikā nandirāgasahagatā tatratatrābhinandinī, seyyathidaṃ—",
  "sn56.13:6.3": "kāmataṇhā, bhavataṇhā, vibhavataṇhā.",
  "sn56.13:6.4": "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhasamudayaṃ ariyasaccaṃ.",
  "sn56.13:7.1": "Katamañca, bhikkhave, dukkhanirodhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ?",
  "sn56.13:7.2": "Yo tassāyeva taṇhāya asesavirāganirodho cāgo paṭinissaggo mutti anālayo—",
  "sn56.13:7.3": "idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhanirodhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ.",
  "sn56.13:8.1": "Katamañca, bhikkhave, dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ?",
  "sn56.13:8.2": "Ayameva ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo, seyyathidaṃ—",
  "sn56.13:8.3": "sammādiṭṭhi … pe …",
  "sn56.13:8.4": "sammāsamādhi—",
  "sn56.13:8.5": "idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ.",
  "sn56.13:8.6": "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri ariyasaccāni.",
  "sn56.13:9.1": "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe …",
  "sn56.13:9.2": "‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti.",
  "sn56.13:10.1": "Tatiyaṃ."
}